projects.description: A stored set of quotes is randomly iterated through and displayed, either automatically or by user input.
Pulling from an array of fictional students, this project demonstrates the generation of display pages and the ability to cycle through them.
This project explores the use of form validation, user selective input, and filtered options in dropdown menus.
Using the classic 'Connect Four' game, this project explores the possibiliites of Object Oriented Programming.
Using the randomuser.me API this project demonstrates sending fetch() requests, the use of modal windows, and cycling through listed items via user input.
